        "article_content_DtmPph": {
          "type": "article_content",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>It’s a reality that baffles Purdy Rubin and Charlotte Figg, co-founders of the eponymously named natural cleaning brand Purdy & Figg. “We’d been cleaning naturally for years before we developed Counter Clean,” says Charlotte, “it was our way of finding the joy in cleaning, and caring deeply for our homes.” And that’s really what sets Purdy & Figg apart.</p><p>Yes, they help to reduce plastic waste, harsh chemicals and synthetic fragrances, but they also help transform cleaning from a chore to a joy. “All with one simple spray for your whole home, that looks just as good as it smells,” Charlotte adds with a conspiratorial wink. </p><p>“Fragrance is essential to us,” adds aromatherapy-enthusiast Purdy. “Our perfumers blend new, limited-edition scents every few months that move in step with the season.” Calabrian Lemon is their latest summer-ready scent, which, by the smell of it, will soon join the brand’s Hall of Fame alongside member favourites like Patchouli & Cedarwood, Geranium & Ylang Ylang, and Rose & Violet.</p>",
            "content_class": "",
            "content_text-color": "#616161"
          }
        },
        "article_quote_qymPDW": {
          "type": "article_quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "“From sun-soaked Calabria<span style=\"display: block\">with love”</span>",
            "quote-mobile": "“From sun-soaked Calabria with love”"
          }
        },
