        "article_content_bMGnQE": {
          "type": "article_content",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>“Natural surfactants work a bit like soap. They break down bacteria and lift away the grime they cling to.” It’s a completely different approach to chemical cleaning sprays, but a worthy switch when it comes to detoxifying our spaces and caring properly for our surfaces.</p><p>Aside from a few natural stone surfaces that need special treatment, Counter Clean is effortlessly effective throughout the home. That means one beautiful spray can replace your surface cleaner, glass spray, bleach, and more.</p><p>“All you’ve got to do is add water,” Purdy adds. “You’ll start with a gorgeous glass Bottle for Life you’ll be proud to show off, a microfibre cloth, and three scent refills. Fill your bottle with your first scent, shake it well, and get cleaning. You won’t look back.”</p>",
            "content_class": "",
            "content_text-color": "#616161"
          }
        },
